CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 13, 1957, pg. 3 reads: "Notables Honor Athletes - Among those participating on the Kay Boys Club's program for the granting of athletic awards to members were (left to right) Judge Louis L. Kaufman, of Allegheny County Court; Bailey Gordon, Kay Club board member; Atty. Everett E. Utterback, assistant administrator of the Pittsburgh Housing Authority; Atty. William F. McCrady and Maurice B. Cohill, board members. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Judge Louis L. Kaufman, Bailey Gordon, Atty. Everett E. Utterback, Atty. William F. McCrady, and Maurice B. Cohill, posed in interior, possibly Kay Boy's Club, with two toned walls
